creator: APS Bank plc
descriptionHtml:
The myAPS mobile banking app makes your everyday banking easy, quick & secure. You can use it anytime and anywhere.

Features include
• Manage your personal and business accounts
• Swipe easily to see account balances
• Transfer money between accounts
• Make transfers and payments
• Create payment templates and standing orders
• Carry out mobile payments

Getting started
In order to use the myAPS app you must be an APS Bank customer and sign up for the internet and mobile banking service through www.apsbank.com.mt. Once the sign up is done, you’re ready to go!

Help
Should you have any queries, you may:
Call us on 2122 6644
Ask at your nearest APS Branch
descriptionShort: The myAPS application allows you to manage your accounts from your phone.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: This new release will make your communication with APS more personal and secure. Thank you for using myAPS!
